The Indicator.R script is used to read in data for the various indicators to be used for the SDM. These are then cropped to the target region and saved in .tif format in the folder data/indicator_stack/ for later use. As the process for some of the bigger files takes a lot of time, ready to use indicator .tif files are to be found in the aformentioned folder.
